[%cal Gf4c7,Gf4h6]} Kg7 28. Qg3 Rac8 29. Nd4 {[%csl Ra6,Rb7,Rc6,Gd4,Gg3][%cal
Gd4f5] The rearrangement is finished. White has a strategically winning
