Ng6 Bxg6 20. Bxg6 f5 {[%csl Rg6]} 21. g3 Qf6 22. Bh5 e5 $1 23. dxe5 Bxe5 $11 {
and black equalized the game in 0-1 Bukavshin,I (2506)-Kovalenko,I (2567)/
