promising here} 13... h6 14. Nxd4 Qh4 (14... Nf6 15. Bb2 Nxd5 16. Nf5 Bxf5 17.
Bxf5 $16 {[%csl Gb2,Gf5][%cal Ga1d1,Gf1e1] is a dream position for white.}) 15.
