21. Bxd5 $146 Bxd5 22. Ng5 $3 $16 Qxg5 23. Rg4 $18) {As usual, we continue
normal development without too much subtleties:} 9. b3 b6 {Presumably, this is
why black played 8...h6 in the first place.} (9... Qe7 {is too sophisticated.
There is no clear reason for black to play like this, other than avoiding
