developing move.} ({Immediately} 14... c5 {is bad on the account of} 15. Bxb7
Qxb7 16. d5 $16 {[%csl Gd5][%cal Gb2g7]}) ({Black can also play} 14... Nf6 15.
Bd3 Ng4 ({and again} 15... c5 {is not good, but this time because of} 16. d5
