18. Bxf6 gxf6 19. cxd5 Rfe8 20. Rxe8+ Rxe8 21. Bb5 Rd8 22. Qf5 $40 {1/2-1/2 
(38) Gerasimchuk,Y-Weber,K (2302) ICCF email 2006}) 17. Re2 Be7 {[%cal Gc6c5]
also failed to equalize.} 18. Qc1 $1 {[%cal Gc1h6] A deep move by strong GM
