Kharitonov,A (2540)-Yasinsky,V (2305)/Moscow 1996/CBM 056 Extra/[Kharitonov] 
(29)}) 14. Nxd4 {[%csl Gf5][%cal Gd4f5] Square f5 is the Achilles heel of
