exd4 Nb6 17. Rfe1 {[%csl Rc8] We have reached one of the most important
positions in the 10...Qe7 line. With accurate play black achieved a solid
position and is one move away from completing development. However, his
light-squared bishop is still a bit problematic. It is not surprising, then,
that black hopes to equalize with} Bxf5 (17... Nbd5 {makes sense as well} 18.
