} 14... exd4 $1 15. Nxf8 dxc3 16. Ng6 {black can make things really messy with}
c5 $1 $132 {[%csl Rg6][%cal Gc5c4]}) 15. dxe5 Bxe5 16. Nxe5 Qxe5 17. e4 $1 {
